title: Sunny Two bedroom Garden Apartment
posting_body: QR Code Link to This Post   Sunny, Bucktown garden apartment with 550 sq. ft. with two bedrooms, LR, Kitchen and Bath. Includes dishwasher, new windows, and brand-new penthouse laundry facilities. Nice backyard that is great for outdoor barbeque and lawn furniture. Easy street parking. Secure bike storage is also available. No pets but a cat is OK. Credit references required. Rent is $1040 and tenant pays Heat and Electric. If you are interested in this opportunity, don't waste time using email. Instead please call Bill for an appointment at (773) 525-2675.
